text: Jupiter is a town in Palm Beach County, Florida, USA. It is named after the Roman god Jupiter. The town is a suburb of Miami. According to the United States census, there were 61,047 people living in Jupiter in 2020. Some famous people who were born in or lived in Jupiter are: Tori Amos, Celine Dion, and Burt Reynolds. ==References== ==Other websites== * Jupiter official website * Jupiter Florida Online Guide * Jupiter Tequesta Juno Beach Chamber of Commerce * Jupiter Courier Newspaper * Jupiter GIS Map * Florida Atlantic University * Jupiter Lighthouse Pictures * Jupiter Florida Category:Towns in Florida Category:Palm Beach County, Florida
